      <p>The full pension increase from 1 April 2015 is 2.3%.
</p>
<p>This is based on the rise in the Retail Price Index over the 12 months to September 2014.</p>
<p>Depending on the period of membership of the TfL Pension Fund, your pension may comprise of various components, some of which are not increased by the Fund at the above rate, but may be increased by the State.</p>
